IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.views WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.V_RptParcelLevel_CENSorter') )
    DROP VIEW dbo.V_RptParcelLevel_CENSorter
GO

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[V_RptParcelLevel_CENSorter]

AS 


SELECT 
lms_cenplclpnrouting_id as id
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_autosystemid
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_lpn
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_status
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_datereceived
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_dateupdated
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_plcdivertid
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_cldivertid
,lms_cenplclpnrouting_divertdescription
,lms_parcel_orderbillcustname
,lms_parcel_orderdelivercustcref
,lms_parcel_orderdelivercustname
,lms_parcel_orderdelivercustsrouteid
FROM dbo.RptParcelLevel 
WHERE lms_cenplclpnrouting_id IS NOT NULL
